title: Bean Broker Coffee House
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, American, Beer/Wine, Bakery, Catering, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. A coffee house and a pub with a laid-back vintage Bohemian vibe and free Wi-Fi. Live music some evenings. Menu changes regularly, usually has a vegetarian or vegan dish; if not, will happily make something. Soy milk is available for coffee drinks.
venueHours: Mon-Tue 6:30am-8:00pm, Wed 6:30am-10:00pm, Thu 6:30am-8:00pm, Fri 6:30am-11:00pm, Sat 6:30am-8:00pm, Sun 8:00am-5:00pm
